title: Launch button takes between 30 seconds and 2 minutes to open and then cannot accept EULA
body: Recently my lol client has been taking a few minutes to open after pressing the launch button. I searched online for a solution and found none so I stuck with it. Until this patch. It takes the same amount of time to pop up but now I have to accept the EULA. After I press accept it instantly closes and does not let me into the client. I can spam launch all day after this and the same thing pops up. Extremely frustrating and I can't even play at all. Any help would be appreciated.

replies.body: Yes I do have bitdefender 2015. My windows 10 install broke my 2013 version without me noticing and I only reinstalled it a week ago so this is probably it. I have tried messing with some settings but no luck so far.
